  "description": {
    "zh": "所以我们要在这里开启大篇章了？那我们继续，好吗？突击步枪可能只是你在塔科夫这里看到的最常见的武器类型，毕竟它们从某个角度看就是样样都好，短距离、长距离、全自动高射速，你能想到的都有。但我觉得我们应该从小而简单开始。\n\n和往常一样，我给你所有你现在需要测试的枪支清单。其中有一些经典款。你可以随便选哪款SCAR步枪，它们本质上都是一样的，至少在我看来……\n我以前有个朋友，他在合同战争升级前选择加入了USEC，总是跟我讲他的步枪收藏，里面全是西方无托式步枪。说实话挺不错的。但我们不是来这里收集文物什么的，你知道该怎么做。",
    "en": "So we're opening the big chapter here? Let's move on then, shall we? Assault rifles might just be the most common type of weapon you're seeing here in Tarkov, after all they are just good at everything from a certain point of view, short ranges, long ranges, fully automatic with high firerate, you name it. But I think we should begin this small and simple.\n\nAs always, I'm giving you the list of all the guns you'll need to test for now. We got some classics among it. You can pick whatever SCAR rifle you want, they are all essentially the same, at least to my eye...\nI had this friend once, he chose to join USEC right before the contract wars escalated, always told me about his rifle collection, it was full of western bullpups. Pretty neat stuff if I'm honest. But we're not here to collect artifacts or anything, you know what to do."
  },
